TY  - JOUR
T1  - Monetary Policy Rules Work and Discretion Doesn’t: A Tale of Two Eras
AU  - TAYLOR, JOHN B.
Y1  - 2012/09/01
PY  - 2012
DA  - 2012/09/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1538-4616.2012.00521.x
